data.description: Located in the charming Silver Hills subdivision, 200 High Pointe Ridge in Prattville, AL, is a stately residence offering spacious and luxurious living. Built in 2001, this property boasts of over 4,000 square feet on a 0.41-acre corner lot, providing ample room both inside and out.  The house features a well-appointed floor plan with four bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms. The interior is highlighted by an open layout that seamlessly connects the living spaces, making it ideal for entertaining and family gatherings. The kitchen is amazing and includes so many features and modern amenities, including a breakfast bar, gas cooktop stove, new convection oven, warming drawer, main refrigerator and beverage refrigerator, and an adjacent eat-in dining area perfect for casual meals.  The expansive master suite offers a private retreat with a large garden tub, separate stand-in shower, dual vanities, and TWO closets. Additional bedrooms are generously sized, suitable for children's rooms, guest accommodations, or home offices.  The upstairs includes two bonus rooms, which can be used for extra family space or additional bedding.  Outdoor living is equally impressive with a covered patio and a stunning in-ground pool set within an expanded fully fenced yard for privacy. This outdoor space is perfect for relaxing or hosting events.  Additional features include a two-car garage, a laundry room with built-in cabinets for extra storage, and a cozy fireplace in the living area, and an additional partially finished converted attic space.  Schools nearby include Daniel Pratt Elementary School, Prattville Junior High, and Prattville High School, adding to the family-friendly appeal of the location?. This residence is not just a house but a warm and inviting home ready to be enjoyed by its new owners.  Schedule your own personal tour today!
